Archipelago, a.k.a War Scrabble
===============================

This is an ocaml implementation (well, will be!) of Archipelago, a Scrabble
like game invented by KirarinSnow.

Rules for the game can be found at:
http://www.kirarinland.com/archipelagorules2.txt

Breakdown of functionality and stuff:

- dictionary
  o load a dictionary (e.g. sowpods)
  o check for valid words
	o optional: load a new dictionary

- game engine
  o create a game instance
	o join a game
	o play a word
	o exchange tiles
	o collect statistics

- web server
